  "title": "LORRY DRIVER",
  "description": "<h3>Driver Responsibilities:</h3><p>Drive long distances to deliver goods to customer place or customer site.</p><p>Load and unload materials not more than 10kg weight.</p><p>Record Materials deliveries and Refuel and clean vehicle.</p><p>Safely transporting goods to and from distribution centers.</p><p>Report road incidents to the dispatcher and Follow traffic laws.</p><p>Follow accident procedures and Keep an activities log and log hours.</p><p>Report mechanical problems to maintenance personnel.</p><p>Plan routes using GPS system ALSO Get goods to the site on time.</p><p>Maintain a positive attitude with customers and team.</p><h3>Driver Requirements:</h3><p>Class 4 driver license.</p><p>Must have clean driving record.</p><p>Able to do overtime and support on public holiidays.</p><p>3+ years' experience as a lorry driver and Good communication skills.</p><p>Ability to drive long distances while maintaining focus and multi trip.</p><p>Must be able to carry 30-50Kg cargos.</p><p>Must be able to do overtime, 24 hours on call.</p>",
